      <title>世界第二大柑橘出口国挑战欧盟限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/south-africa-seeks-talks-with-eu-over-barriers-to-citrus-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，南非已采取初步措施，向世界贸易组织投诉欧盟对其进口柑橘的待遇。]]></description>
